UsageCost: Free first hour then $0.20/kWh from 6am to 6pm Monday to Friday and then $0.10/kWh at all other times (Minimum fee of $1 applies after first hour)

AddressInfo.Title: Adelaide Central Market
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Level 1 - Enter the UPark car park from Grote Street - Turn left at the boom gates and follow aisle left and then straight ahead 100m to east. Look for the overhead indicator lights.

GeneralComments:
Operated by the City of Adelaide using the Chargefox app with contactless (PayWave) payment coming from September 2018
1 hour free parking and charging then normal UPark parking fees and City of Adelaide EV service fees apply
Group of 10 plus 1 charger servicing two accessible parking bays
